<emphasis id="8E0592EDD2EFC3942EB78B75E79202AB" italics="true" pageId="87" pageNumber="88">Pastore</emphasis>
1262), Chile, Uruguay (
<emphasis id="C9204C6E3C053B21E3E03B06DF7D290E" italics="true" pageId="87" pageNumber="88">Gibert</emphasis>
40); Brazil (fide 
<bibRefCitation id="743AA36BCF569E6E05E1A0AF2EC68781" author="O'Donell, CA" journalOrPublisher="Lilloa" pageId="208" pageNumber="209" pagination="87 - 348" refId="B248" refString="O'Donell, CA, 1959. Convolvulaceas argentinas II. Lilloa 29: 87 - 348" title="Convolvulaceas argentinas II." volume="29" year="1959">
<normalizedToken id="3D66A999D0C170F633B7D332A8F3D018" originalValue="O’Donell">O'Donell</normalizedToken>
1959
</bibRefCitation>
: 284); Bolivia (
<emphasis id="CC4D7E9B4D2163C316E4D1397CFB2050" italics="true" pageId="87" pageNumber="88">Wood</emphasis>
22627, 
<emphasis id="728F1A965097A4093F9F1382E3051561" italics="true" pageId="87" pageNumber="88">Bang</emphasis>
